the replacement of the thruster will not jeopardize discoverys 
scheduled launch with the sunprobing ulysses satellite in october 
malone said the damaged thruster was being returned to the 
manufacturer for repairs 
nasa officials believe that on atlantis hydrogen is escaping 
from a flange on the external tank side of a 17inchdiameter 
valve the valve is in a pipe that carries fuel from the tank to 
the main engines 
